'''伯明翰博物館和美術館'''（{{lang-en|Birmingham Museum and Art Gallery}}，'''BM&AG'''）是位於[[英國|英國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]]城市[[伯明翰|伯明翰]]的一座博物館和美術館。博物館內收藏有來自世界各地的眾多各種不同類型的藏品<ref>{{cite book|last=Fisher|first=Mark|authorlink=Mark Fisher (politician)|title=Britain's Best Museums and Galleries: From the Greatest Collections to the Smallest Curiosities|url=https://archive.org/details/britainsbestmuse0000fish|year=2005|publisher=Penguin Books|location=Harmondsworth|isbn=0-14-101960-3|pages=[https://archive.org/details/britainsbestmuse0000fish/page/205 205]–207|chapter=Barber Institute of Fine Arts}}</ref>。博物館現在由伯明翰博物館信託管理<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.commercialnewsmedia.com/archives/16955|title=West Mids accountants appointed by largest independent museums trust|accessdate=2013-08-04|date=2013-07-22|publisher=Commercial News Media|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422081145/http://www.commercialnewsmedia.com/archives/16955|dead-url=no}}</ref>。博物館平時免費開放，但有時舉辦特展時需收取費用。

